<l>yakara viṟuti vēṟṟumaip poruḷvayiṉ</l>
<l>valleḻut tiyaiyi ṉavveḻuttu mikumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The final [nasal] of the word <foreign xml:lang="ta">poṉ</foreign> ' gold ' is dropped,</l>
<l>and <foreign xml:lang="ta">la</foreign> plus <foreign xml:lang="ta">m</foreign> are inserted after it ; this change</l>
<l>occurs only in poetry.<note
              place="foot">e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">poṉ + cuṭar &gt; polañcuṭar</foreign> ' the splendour of gold '.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
